rency-20200427%2F5393844.html&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=7ca716b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/china-to-test-its-digital-currency-20200427/5393844.html</a><br />\n<br />\n賓夕法尼亞沃頓商學院(Wharton School of Business) 教授凱文&middot;沃巴赫(Kevin Webach) 對美國之音說，從這個意義上來看，中國的數字貨幣使用了<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>部分</strong></span></span>區塊鏈科技，然而它不能被稱為一種虛擬貨幣。<br />\n沃巴赫教授說:&ldquo;這種數字貨幣將使用區塊鏈的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>部分</strong></span></span>安全技術, 然而由於這並不是像比特幣這樣使用無許可的區塊鏈進行供應，而是由中央銀行進行統一發行管控，它最多只能說是受到了虛擬貨幣的啟發&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"cbba7206004b03f252c1df99703fb6d3bd8b9a55","tid":1980390,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ef799c21036f676daeba9c1f497940f2bcedcb","tid":1980390,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e9ba2efc67bb4197c038503a226b59daeb940e6","tid":1980390,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcfc8ebdf922cc158c832d03c81d7b84d14b6e33","tid":1980390,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:48:31.000Z","msg":"Blockchain無法控制和修改，但可以監視"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:49:17.000Z","msg":"咁就入唔到支那, 完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"但好處係 blockchain可以防hack"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:34:28.000Z","msg":"防hack d 日本bitcoin 比黑客爆晒d錢啦"},{"pid":"8bd8d45cf31d8e3b05e0d21287d36d6715217bb3","tid":1980390,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:35:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fa3a7755a91fe71abeb32529c4d932f9014aaa9","tid":1980390,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a558fcec73dbb3974830a8e735e5fbe6e173875a","tid":1980390,"uid":199868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab2dff3acc29db0fd97900b6fe2bc06b0ea51d52","tid":1980390,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af1846ab82606a5f3a9a4a52a